author: conor
msg: Fix up Jars so that the first two entries are always the META-INF directory
and the manifest itself. This is not really documented as a Jar requirement
that I am aware of but the JarInputStream code certainly requires this.

msg: Removed redundent access specifiers so that Ant compiles cleanly in jikes pedantic mode. They are "strongly discouraged" by the JLS spec.
